    "name": "Twin Stick Heroes 2",
    "steam_appid": 2330660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twin Stick Heroes 2 is a top down arena shooter.  Choose from a diverse cast of heroes, and engage in epic battles across a galaxy of exotic planets. This time with new gameplay options an array of new heroes to master, and balance improvements for fair and thrilling combat.  Twin Stick Heroes 2 is the sequel you've been waiting for. Are you ready to prove your skills and conquer the cosmos?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >             Join the fight today!<strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/a8241e97ad5f5afdd474c7dfe8da82fe.avif?t=1769407786\" width=616 height=152 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                        WELCOME TO TWIN STICK COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b9a213285bc1f306228e9125e13f81ac.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b9a213285bc1f306228e9125e13f81ac.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b9a213285bc1f306228e9125e13f81ac.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At its core Twin Stick Heroes 2 is a hilarious and intense 1-4 player party game. The &quot;heroes&quot; cater towards very different playstyles, learning which one suites you best is key. Combat can seem wild and unpredictable with everchanging items and stages, but mastering your hero will carry you through to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/729cab374b2723d635a91d9e4f3f07da.avif?t=1769407786\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR HERO</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A VIBRANT CAST OF 27 HEROS! </i>Every hero in the game has specific strengths and weaknesses, learning to master their weapon and abilities<br>is key to victory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>MASTERY SYSTEM! </i>Play against your friends to unlock new stages and heroes', or go it alone against bosses to unlock their mastery skin and furnish your home</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>ITEMS ARE COMING OUT OF MY EARS!</i> Make use of the weird items and wield abilities never before seen, such as the timeline changing<br>save state, or the black hole which is so powerful it may eat everyone on stage!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>WATCH THE SKIES!</i> A new weather mode can be enabled to unleash even more havoc in the match! Don't let the wind blow you away, and make sure to  keep your eyes to the sky and nab items with the item shower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/6f8f2db8ef4374ea12dc4cc987c2f0c8.avif?t=1769407786\" width=616 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b2df7cc9366f1f5eb803f889efbe2d82.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=608 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b2df7cc9366f1f5eb803f889efbe2d82.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/b2df7cc9366f1f5eb803f889efbe2d82.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Say hello to a new and improved cast of &quot;heroes&quot;.  Take on your foes as the otherworldly Hunam, showcasing inhuman sniping skills. Defend your position like a pro with the dependable Camper, or dispense unrelenting justice as the battle-hardened Veteran.  Or pull out all the stops with the evil mind manipulator himself Dr Brain and his sinister goons! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/2590fdee4b927bd8318a544516668405.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=614 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/2590fdee4b927bd8318a544516668405.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/2590fdee4b927bd8318a544516668405.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A TRUE PIXEL ART EXPERIENCE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art was inspired from the likes of older snes games such as Earthbound and FZERO, mixed with a healthy dose of Saturday morning cartoons such as Beavis and Butthead and King of the Hill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight on the labyrinthine surface of Gord City, whose asphalt paved roads and buildings make for a unique experience, or journey across the coliseum which is littered with the megalithic remains of a once mighty civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/22911f1efaf416a04d1537ebf0a8bcb0.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/22911f1efaf416a04d1537ebf0a8bcb0.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/22911f1efaf416a04d1537ebf0a8bcb0.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SINGLE PLAYER!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat evil bosses which vary from a fungal infection to a gangster mob</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hero masteries that unlock costumes which carry over into multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new furniture for your home in the single player mode<br> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/5d1592b39ec3ac28a16a5a9125eac90f.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/5d1592b39ec3ac28a16a5a9125eac90f.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/5d1592b39ec3ac28a16a5a9125eac90f.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >local multiplayer, and online multiplayer with Steam remote play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new and improved single player experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >27 Heroes to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mastery system and tons of unlocks to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items galore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of handcrafted stages to fight on</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cartoony snes inspired pixel art</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.poster.avif?t=1769407786\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.webm?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330660/extras/4a410b2056c6e192878df404069974e3.mp4?t=1769407786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
